1367,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d2360726-Reviews-or1365-Mercure_London_Kensington-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Mercure London Kensington Hotel Reviews,This is a con!,"This ""hotel"" pretends to be 4 star - but it is not. There is no restaurant, no room service, the receptionist is always alone, and the rooms are very small, windows cannot open, and the noise from the communicating doors make for a terrible night's sleep. Best avoided! They charge 4 star rates though. Do not stay here. The Premier across the road has larger beds, better rooms, at around half the price.",Date of stay: September 2010,1.0
